{"tid":1799789,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳朗昇指不能接受警員鏡頭前展示身分證稍後會投訴","createTime":"2019-12-27T08:16:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T08:35:14.000Z","uid":152476,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b2f968383e2f53beb6fd6d409f4c7ef59cb8a5b8","tid":1799789,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T08:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1499802_1_20191227154931.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1499802_1_20191227154931.jpg&h=272283c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》記者陳朗昇昨日在大埔超級城直播採訪期間，被警員截查並搜查身分證，有警員在直播鏡頭前一度展示記者的記者證及身分證。陳朗昇接受本台查詢時說，當時與幾名新界北刑事總部警員發生口角，指他阻差辦公，被要求取出身分證。期間有警員叫他繼續攝錄，並將他的身分證及記者證展示在鏡頭前，陳朗昇要求警員停止，但對方稱是記者決定直播。<br />\n<br />\n陳朗昇說，有關警員沒有佩戴行動呼號卡，委任證亦沒有放在當眼位置，因此不清楚對方的身分。<br />\n<br />\n他批評警員行為不恰當及不能接受，知法犯法。自己正執行記者的職責，受基本法保障，又指當時有幾千人收看直播，警員向公眾展示他的個人資料，是超越「不完美、可改善」的程度，稍後會到私隱專員公署及投訴警察課投訴。<br />\n<br />\n陳朗昇說，早前有部分個人資料已被洩漏，曾每日收到十多個滋擾電話，擔心身分證號碼被展示，有人會借他的資料進行借貸。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499802-20191227.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499802-20191227.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=TEMpI0ru4fZij%2BnpPgfFHWDcYOQIx6XO0JIcXsozN2c%3D&h=f81a4e21\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499802-20191227.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=11f2e5cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499802-20191227.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n昇哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e7f3bf7b21187b8568b2916875a92e9defd8c1","tid":1799789,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T08:17:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02ac6998855d18cf1678e191afd880e3ddb2ddc6","tid":1799789,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T08:21:36.000Z","msg":"撐昇哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af7c43eab78c127a06c40e2a9cc96e02b66324b6","tid":1799789,"uid":69741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T08:23:38.000Z","msg":"之前話讀名校被雞姦個男仔1都話之後會出嚟爆詳情，無哂影都唔知係咪浮咗屍<br />\n希望佢講真，唔驚被恐嚇威脅都堅持煮死隻1狗1啦"},{"pid":"03a837d8f6598dde19639ecec60ffaf2d2362d5c","tid":1799789,"uid":278733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T08:35:14.000Z","msg":"支持昇哥！"}]}